title: fil1p
author: fil1p
content: Hello everyone!I'm writing this post to see if there are any builders here who could use a development fund?Dev company Blank offers 50,000 euros in development services, so if someone is building something, it's a shame to miss out.If you need more information - https://blankhq.co/web3-developer-fundOr join the Discord channel - http://discord.gg/tm32Y3uMQCThanks, and good luck if anyone decides to apply!

comments.author: Joel_Jantsen
comments.body: Does the project have to be web3 only? Could it be anything else that is general tech/SAAS?

comments.author: OgNasty
comments.body: I’m not sure this thread is in the right section. This being a Bitcoin forum, things like web3 usually can not be found in the main sections of the forum. Your typically have to look to the altcoin section for this sort of thing, so perhaps if you aren’t getting the engagement you desired, you could attempt to make a thread somewhere there.
